dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data layer is for use in generalized mapping applications. It is intended to show all of the roads (Federal, State, County, County Forest, Town, Municipal and Private) in Marinette County. The data layer is intended for use with GIS software.]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2018.[This data layer is a centerline Personal Geodatabase Feature Class of the roads in Marinette County. Data is referenced to the Marinette County Coordinate System, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
